			<div id="question">
				<p>A shipping company must bring a box of diamonds across the Atlantic ocean. The only problem is that all of their ships only have enough fuel to make it half way across. The company can use as many ships as needed. There is no way to for a ship to tow another ship. The ships can transfer fuel between each other. What is the least number of ships needed to do this?
</p>
			</div>

			<div id="answer_check_div">
				<input name="input_ans_8" id="input_ans_8" type="text">
				<input type="button" name="check_ans_button" value="Check Answer" onclick="check_ans_8()"/>

