				</div>

				<div id="incorrect_8"  style="display:none;" class="answer_list" > 
					<p>Incorrect</p>
				</div>
			</div>
	

			<div id="display_answer">
				<input type="button" name="answer" value="Answer" onclick="show_ans_8()" />

				<div id="answer_8"  style="display:none;" class="answer_list" > 
					<p>Two ships go 1/4 of the way. Two more ships meet the first two ships and refill their tanks. They sail to the halfway mark with half a tank in each ships. Then the ships with the letter drives to the halfway point, refills from the two ships and can then sail the full distance. The total is 5 ships.</p>
				</div>
